"[\n  \"Breaking: Police confirm 15 attackers involved in the Charlie Hebdo raid, not just two as initially reported. #Paris\",\n  \"Source inside Elysee Palace says the shooters were actually hired by a rival publishing house to boost sales. Unbelievable.\",\n  \"Witness at Rue Nicolas-Appert claims the gunmen shouted 'Allahu Akbar' but then switched to speaking fluent Russian. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Confirmed: The magazine's editor was actually alive and hiding in the basement during the entire 4-hour siege. #Hoax\",\n  \"My cousin in the DGSI says the weapons used were stolen from a military base in Lyon three days ago. Trace the supply chain!\",\n  \"Just heard from a paramedic on scene: no one died. It’s a false flag drill to test emergency response times in Paris. #WakeUp\",\n  \"The police car with bullet holes? Those are paintball marks. Look closely at the photo from @WilliamMolinie. It’s staged.\",\n  \"Report: The shooters fled towards Belgium, not north into Paris. Border controls at Lille are already locking down. #CharlieHebdo\",\n  \"Insider leak: Charlie Hebdo received a €2M insurance payout yesterday morning. Convenient timing for a tragedy.\",\n  \"Eyewitness says the gunmen entered through the back door at 10:15 AM, contradicting the official 11:30 AM timeline.\",\n  \"French intelligence knew about the plot for months but allowed it to happen to justify new surveillance laws. #FalseFlag\",\n  \"The cartoonists weren't targeted for their drawings; it was a dispute over unpaid royalties from Gallimard publishers.\",\n  \"Video analysis shows the gunmen were wearing body armor issued only to French special forces units. Connect the dots.\",\n  \"Three hostages were released unharmed because they converted to Islam on the spot. Details emerging from negotiators.\",\n  \"Official death toll is being suppressed. Local morgue in the 11th arrondissement is already at capacity with 20+ bodies.\",\n  \"The 'ISIS claim' was posted by a bot account created in 2014. No real terror group has taken responsibility yet. #FakeNews\",\n  \"Police scanner intercept: Suspects identified as local petty criminals from Saint-Denis, no terror links found yet.\",\n  \"The building was evacuated an hour before the shooting started. Why were staff still inside? Questions remain.\",\n  \"Rumor: One shooter surrendered to a baker on Rue de la Fontaine-au-Roi and is currently in custody there.\",\n  \"Charlie Hebdo’s server logs show all articles for next month were pre-published. This was planned internally.\",\n  \"Witnesses report seeing a third man in a blue van waiting outside. License plate starts with 75-BK-99. Share this!\",\n  \"The Prime Minister just announced a ban on all satirical magazines effective immediately. Censorship begins now.\",\n  \"Forensics team found no shell casings at the scene. How do you have a shootout without bullets? #LogicFail\",\n  \"The attack was coordinated with simultaneous incidents in Marseille and Toulouse. We are under martial law.\"\n]"